    "region in Australia by four indexes:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **IRSD** — Index of Relative Socio-economic Disadvantage (most commonly used)\n",
    "- **IRSAD** — Index of Relative Socio-economic Advantage and Disadvantage  \n",
    "- **IER** — Index of Economic Resources  \n",
    "- **IEO** — Index of Education and Occupation\n",
    "\n",
    "A low IRSD score = high disadvantage. We will use IRSD as a key feature \n",
    "in our classification model.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Source:** ABS — abs.gov.au"
   ]
